## Who is the traitor?

So, from a purely mathematical point of view, can we determine who is most likely to be the traitor?

We're assuming that no one is lying, so this metaphor doesn't really hold up, but please bear with me.

### Pick the traitor

Use the diagram below to click on the person that you suspect to be the traitor. Click on the circle in the diagram so that you person you suspect is added to the guilty looking box. If you change your mind, simply click on them again to remove them from the box.

